devdoc.details: This contract allows users to buy shirts of different sizes and colors.

buyShirt(uint8,uint8).details: Allows users to buy a shirt of a specific size and color by paying the correct amount.

getShirtPrice(uint8,uint8).details: Returns the price of a shirt based on its size and color.

returns._0: The price of the shirt in wei.

getShirts(uint8,uint8).details: Returns the number of shirts owned by the caller of a specific size and color.

returns._0: The count of shirts of the specified size and color owned by the caller.
